<ul>
<li><b>Confirmation Ticket:</b> Please print this email and bring it with you along with your photo ID on the day of your tour.</li>
<li>
    <b>Arrival:</b>  Please plan to arrive 15 minutes prior to your tour time to allow for check-in at the Chick-fil-A security entrance. When you arrive on campus, you will check-in with our 
    security guard (in the left lane) to confirm your tour and registered # of guests. <span style="font-weight:bold;">Please note that each person in your tour group, regardless of age, must be previously registered on our 
    website to receive admittance onto the Chick-fil-A campus and tour.</span> You will receive a pass for your car and further directions on parking and entering the tour entrance. 
    Click <a href=@(baseurl + "/Areas/tours/Content/Doc/directions.pdf")>HERE</a> for directions to our campus.
</li>
<li>
    <b>Check-In:</b> As you face the building, look to your right for the directional sign, "Chick-fil-A Home Office Backstage Tour Entrance" 
    (the sign will be to the left of the tiered waterfalls). Walk along this path and through the grassy area, and then you will see a red 
    carpet as you approach the double doors located on the right side of the main building. Please go inside and check-in at the welcome desk. 
</li>
<li><b>Age Requirements:</b> We require that all guests be six years of age or older due to the amount of walking throughout the tour experience.</li>
<li><b>Attire:</b> The Chick-fil-A<sup>®</sup> Home Office Backstage Tour requires a lot of walking, so please wear comfortable shoes. Business casual or casual attire is preferred.</li>
<li><b>Don’t Forget:</b> Remember to come prepared to have FUN! The Chick-fil-A Cows and the Chick-fil-A family eagerly await your arrival!</li>
</ul>
