    <a href="mailto:homeofficebackstagetour@chick-fil-a.com">homeofficebackstagetour@chick-fil-a.com</a> or 404-530-1854. <span style="font-weight:bold;">Please note that no additional guests can be added within 72 hours of your tour reservation.</span>
</p>
<br/>
<p>It is our pleasure to host you,<br /> The Chick-fil-A<sup>®</sup> Home Office Backstage Tour Team</p>
